\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Could you tell me the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes, in Waller Street. Alderness Road, Hull.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Do you know how many years you lived in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh no, I can't tell - oh well I live all me school days there. And then I went to live with our old doctor. Doctor }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 Hollingsworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926  who lived on - Alderness Road. But - his house is pulled down now you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 So all the years that you lived with your parents were spent at Waller Street, in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh no, we lived in Victor Street and then we lived on Newbridge Road, and then we lived in Brindley - Street. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 Waller Street then Victor Street?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
Yes. And then - and then Newbridge Road. And then - have you put Brindley Street down? Yes. New - you've put Newbridge Road? And then Brindley Street. And that's where my parents died, in Brindley Stree
t. And it's right up where East Park Hall it was - East Park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 So in about twelve or thirteen years you lived in about four different houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Do you remember why your family made these moves, was it to get in a bigger house or was it for more convenience of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Well I suppose it was the bigger family because it was only a little small house you know, just two }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 bed roomed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926  house. Waller Street, it was tiny house. I - I dreamt about it the other day and I couldn't imagine how - we all got in there you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 You think that all the moves were to accommodate the growing family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 There was - there was twelve of us, six boys and six girls. Yes, and one sister died when 
she was about eight. And a little brother died when he was about - three I think. I can just see him now do you know. He was a lovely corpse really. And I've seen him all me life, isn't it funny. Now me sister wasn't so good because she had - they - they 
call it then consumption of the bowels, but it was - what's the new name they've given consumption of the bowels. No, it hasn't - it hasn't come to me, I can't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Can you remember how your brothers and sisters were spaced, were you the eldest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh no, I'm the eldest but one, I've an older sister than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 How much is there in your sister and you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
There's only a - there's only eleven months between some of us. But then I - I shall have to sit and study it all you know, I couldn't study it n
ow. And then there was a gap between us, now between me and my youngest brother, he lives - did you come - where you live - well, yes, that was his wife, and he's - well he's got a good job at Bradford. But he's lame, he - he has a nerve that stops workin
g and I have the same complaint.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 And it makes him lame?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes, just drag this leg.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 How many years difference would there be in your eldest sister and your youngest brother, from one end of the family to the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Well she would be - oh 
she's living yet you know is me eldest sister. She's - eighty - what month is it now - well now whether she's eighty-one in June or eighty-two I really don't know. She's either eighty-one or eighty-two and I'm - I - there's only about eleven months betwee
n
 us, she was born in June, the fifteenth, and I was born the following July the twenty-second. And then the next sister, well there's a bit more difference between - she lives at - at Wathendon, and I can't tell you how old they are 'cos I can't remember 
you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
How old is the father of the lady who was here, do you know, would there be about twenty years difference between the eldest and the youngest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh yes. Our Lucy - our Lucy - our Louis, he retires in - he's working for the - - for the Nav
y you know, he's got a good job. And he - he retires on a good }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 pension}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
 at - sixty. Now then I don't know whether it's this year he retires or next year, he's on - nearly on retiring age. But it's sixty they retire, not sixty-five like the others you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 So there must be about twenty-one years between your older sister and youngest brother
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Between some of them there's only eleven months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 But between some others there's a rather bigger gap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Just eighteen months or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 When I was born? Oh no. My father was seventy-eight when he died and me mother was seventy-four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 How old were you when they died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh, I don't know. Well now
, I - I - I went to see and - I lived in Oakworth then you know. I often used to go to Hull. 'Cos we could get the cheap weekends and all that you know. No, I don't remember how old I would be when they died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Had your father always lived in Hull or did he come from somewhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh yes, he - they - they both came straight out of the country. My father lived at a little place called Wado}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 th Hill. Wado}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
th Hill. I think now - yes, Wado}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 th Hill, I - I - in Yorkshire, near Hull, Wadorth Hill. And me
 mother was born at Burton Pidsey near Hull. Pidsey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 So they both came from country places just outside Hull?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 They were both country and they came straight to Hull. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
And me father was like only a - a farm sort of hand but he got on very well you 
know, and he was a real good scholar because that youngest brother of mine, he's a good scholar you know, he's had a good education, yes. He helped him with all these contracts he - he did all his pile driving business and all that on the River Humber you
 know. Very good was me father really. But me mother wasn't a really good scholar because - when she used to writ}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5262569\charrsid11078926 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
 to us, if she was - she would put a - not a capital U like sometimes she should do, do just an ordinary u you know. Of course she left school when she was eight you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 So when your father lived in the country at Wado}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5262569\charrsid11078926 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 th Hill he was a farm worker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes, a farm worker, yes. And then he was a pile driver when he finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 When he moved to Hull what did he become, when you were a little girl what was he then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
Well he worked at the gas works at first. Then of course I don't know where he worked because he sort of got on and got on you know. And really when he - when he got some money he - he was a - he was a bit of a boozer wa
s my father when he got into - he got into bad company you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 That was when he was pile driving?
