\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
Well - I didn't know - I went to Hull you see not so long since and I saw this Walle Street where we used to live and I - I - I don't know who I was with, whether I was with me sister or what, I says, re
ally, I says, I don't know how mother did with all us in the little house like that. They were so small I really couldn't - I - I don't know whether - you see, they're back to back houses here but they weren't back to back houses in Hull. They were throug
h houses you see. But - no, I can't tell you much. I don't really remember.
