\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 How many rooms had it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Three bedrooms and a - a sitting room, a livin
g room. And a scullery. And then a little out place. With a lovely garden there as well, we grew roses and everything, it was a lovely house was that. But I was married then you know. I wasn't there then. Yes.
