\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Oh no, I thin
k - no, I think we had a lot of clothes given. We had an aunt in service and she lived with a - a real good family and they'd two in family, two - two girls, he was a Norwegian Consul or something, this is where my aunt lived in service, me mother's siste
r. Now then I believe my mother's sister did live with us a bit as well. But I can't remember really much, I can't remember much about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 This auntie used to get you clothes from this family did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes. Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5262569\charrsid11078926 es}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
. Mrs - Mrs - they called them Mr and Mrs Floddenham, they were Norwegian people you know, but they were lovely and they'd two daughters. And one of the daughters went out of her mind, it was awful sad about her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 And sometimes you would get their clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes. They used to give lovely clothes and me mother could remake them you know. She was a good sewer, yes.
