e the home help your mother to look after her house or family, such as relations or friends or neighbours? Do you remember any relations or friends or neighbours coming into the house to give her a lift?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 No.
