\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
She - she always had the same person as a nurse, she was - I don't know whether she was a proper nurse but - they called her Mrs Coates. But I can't remember - I - I don't seem to remember muc
h about her now, she always had the same woman every - confinement you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 And this lady would come in just to help deliver the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes, and do the work you know. Yes. Oh yes, yes.
