ame now. Just a sewing lady, a little old lady, lovely she was. And I've forgotten her name, oh dear, I wish I could remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 And she taught you sewing?
