\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 You didn't particularly like or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Well I didn't dislike it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 What did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
Yes, well there were some very nice and there were some - there was one teacher we had and oh he was a bad tempered man, Mr Myers. But he wouldn't touch a girl. It was only the boys. And he'd get such a temper he would get his stick and
 he would - throw it from one end of the classroom to the other you know. But he was a good teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Was he at Escort Street school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 I think he must have been at Escort Street school. Yes. Yes.
