Well I don't think so, there were so many of us you know. I can't think they'd - they'd really - well they wouldn't sort of have time I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 You don't remember them asking you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 No I don't remember if they ever -
