}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 Hollingsworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926  was a lady that wasn't - always in bed, I don't know why.
