\insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 Hollingsworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 
 you know, when I gave me notice in - she said, we're thinking of going to Scarborough for a week and I was going to take you. So I said, I don't want to go to Scarborough. So that was the finish and I wouldn't go to Scar
borough with them. I could have gone to Scarborough with them for a week.
