\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 I don't - I don't think I thought anything about it, it was a wage and I used to take it home you see. And I don't -
 I don't think they ever gave me anything back so I don't know whether I ever spent anything, I can't - I - I gave it all to me mother.
