\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes. Yes. She didn't make no difference you know, some - places - you knew you were the maid you see. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
