 sometimes at ten. And sometimes I used to have it with her because that's the time of the - I never liked - I couldn't eat breakfast at eight o'clock. But I enjoyed it at ten if I - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13241232\charrsid11078926 had}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926  it with anybody you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 So cook and you would officially have breakfast at eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6371515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 But you'd have it later with Miss Field?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 Yes.
