I wonder if he would have to - well I should think he would have to do, he'd only one cow you know. No. I know they called him John Tickles and he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7756009\charrsid11078926 nasty}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926  old man. Ooh, horrid, yes.
