\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid223242 EG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11880871\charrsid11078926 No, but there - no, I can't remember any books, I don't
 know whether there was but they'd tons of weekly papers. Magazines, oh galore. Yes, newspapers. Every newspaper there was.
